data.description: Welcome to your Dream Home!! Attention Culinary Enthusiasts, this Beautiful Home boast top the line Stainless Steel Appliances, including 5-Burner Gas Stove with Cast Iron Griddle Insert, Dual Ovens with Convection, true Ventilation Hood, Granite Countertops, Custom Cabinetry.  The addition of Hurricane Impact Windows, and Insulated Hurricane Garage Door ensures safety and peace of mind. A cozy Wood-Burning Fireplace adds Charm and Warmth to the Home. Updated Bathrooms, High Quality Laminate Floors and Brand New Roof, adds value and durability.. This property also comes with a Home Warranty!!  Situated in a Quiet Neighborhood, this Home offers a Tranquil Living Environment while still being Conveniently Located near all Amenities. !!
